=EN>Auno1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 108<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/17/02 5:17:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1138.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Why we love FV</span><hr size=1> Given I admit to being non-RP. Just not good at it.<br>
<br>
